  <section id="about">
    <h2>About the Game</h2>
    <p>
      Young Street Ontario is a realistic open-world Roblox game set in the real city of Ontario, Canada. Inspired by the iconic Yonge Street and the diverse neighborhoods surrounding it, this game lets you explore the urban environment, drive cars, take on jobs, and experience a slice of Canadian city life like never before.
    </p>
  </section>

